This paper deals with natural language processing and text generation, which are core topics in the field of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also focuses on generating teasers for news articles, which involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and social media analysis (cs.SI). Additionally, the paper involves compiling a dataset and evaluating models, which are tasks that fall under the sub-categories of data management (cs.SD) and machine learning (cs.LG).
